<h3 id="inline-form"><a class="header-anchor" href="#inline-form" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Inline form</h3>
<p>When the vertical space is limited and the form is relatively simple, you can put it in one line.</p>
<demo-block class="demo-box" :jsfiddle="{&quot;html&quot;:&quot;&lt;el-form :inline=\&quot;true\&quot; :model=\&quot;formInline\&quot; class=\&quot;demo-form-inline\&quot;&gt;\n  &lt;el-form-item label=\&quot;Approved by\&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;el-input v-model=\&quot;formInline.user\&quot; placeholder=\&quot;Approved by\&quot;&gt;&lt;/el-input&gt;\n  &lt;/el-form-item&gt;\n  &lt;el-form-item label=\&quot;Activity zone\&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;el-select v-model=\&quot;formInline.region\&quot; placeholder=\&quot;Activity zone\&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;el-option label=\&quot;Zone one\&quot; value=\&quot;shanghai\&quot;&gt;&lt;/el-option&gt;\n      &lt;el-option label=\&quot;Zone two\&quot; value=\&quot;beijing\&quot;&gt;&lt;/el-option&gt;\n    &lt;/el-select&gt;\n  &lt;/el-form-item&gt;&lt;el-form-item&gt;\n    &lt;el-button type=\&quot;primary\&quot; @click=\&quot;onSubmit\&quot;&gt;Query&lt;/el-button&gt;\n  &lt;/el-form-item&gt;\n&lt;/el-form&gt;\n\n&quot;,&quot;script&quot;:&quot;\n  export default {\n    data() {\n      return {\n        formInline: {\n          user: '',\n          region: ''\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    methods: {\n      onSubmit() {\n        console.log('submit!');\n      }\n    }\n  }\n&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:null}">
                    <div class="source" slot="source"><el-form :inline="true" :model="formInline" class="demo-form-inline">
